<br>
EQ is designed for UBER/TWINK &quot;kill the Mob over and over&quot; type folks. &quot;power gamers&quot;<br>
<br>
Causual players and small guilds seem to pay the price.  However, Leading a small guild is not difficult if you have good folk in your guild.<br>
<br>
Pick people you have played with.  Pick people you trust and who get along well with other players.  This makes a big difference in smaller guilds.<br>
<br>
It's hard work being a leader, but it's a little easier when you have some really nice folk in the guild.<br>
<br>
